            <div class="aboutText">
                <p>TCB is run by a lady named <b>Patty Scull,</b> who has embraced her oddness and her total obsession with cats. Her writing has appeared in: Brooklyn Vegan, Greenpointers, Short and Sweet NYC, Broke Ass Stuart's Goddamn Website, Stepaway Magazine, Erma Bombeck's HumorWriters.org, and other various places around the web.                 </p>
                <div class="aboutCredentials">
                    <p>Patty is a Professional Member of the <a href="https://catwriters.com/" target="blank">Cat Writer's Association</a>.</p>
                    <img src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/58e534c52e69cfd83dc862d9/1502201313365-2U4WRXKB52196WR5HBUK/cat-writers-association-professional-that-cat-blog-patty-scull?format=300w" alt="">
                </div>
                <p><strong> Thomas the cat</strong>'s writing has appeared in this blog, where he hopes to launch his superstar writing career reviewing things like catnip, cat toys, and proteins in different flavors. </p>
                <p>To submit pitches or just to say “howdy!” please fill out our <a href="../html/contact.html">contact form</a>.</p>
